\begin{abstract}
This document provides an overview of new functionality in XPCE-5. The
highlights are passing native Prolog data through arguments of
Prolog-defined methods, single-file executables using embedded (image)
resources and the introduction of graphical tables.

\Chapref{migrate} provides a checklist for incomatibilities.
\end{abstract}

